graph TB
    subgraph "ODH Model Controller"
        MainController[OpenshiftInferenceService<br/>Reconciler]
        WebhookValidator[Knative Service<br/>Validator Webhook<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS]

        subgraph "Sub-Reconcilers"
            ModelMesh[ModelMesh<br/>Reconciler]
            Serverless[KServe Serverless<br/>Reconciler]
            RawDeploy[KServe Raw<br/>Reconciler]
        end

        StorageReconciler[Storage Secret<br/>Reconciler]
        CAReconciler[Custom CA Cert<br/>Reconciler]
        MonitoringReconciler[Monitoring<br/>Reconciler]
        ModelRegistry[Model Registry<br/>Reconciler]

        MainController -->|delegates| ModelMesh
        MainController -->|delegates| Serverless
        MainController -->|delegates| RawDeploy
    end

    subgraph "Watched CRDs"
        InferenceService[InferenceService<br/>serving.kserve.io/v1beta1]
        ServingRuntime[ServingRuntime<br/>serving.kserve.io/v1alpha1]
        KnativeService[Knative Service<br/>serving.knative.dev/v1]
        DSC[DataScienceCluster<br/>opendatahub.io]
        DSCI[DSCInitialization<br/>opendatahub.io]
    end

    subgraph "Created/Managed Resources"
        Route[OpenShift Routes<br/>443/TCP HTTPS]
        AuthConfig[AuthConfig<br/>Authorino]
        NetworkPolicy[NetworkPolicies<br/>Pod isolation]
        VirtualService[VirtualServices<br/>Istio routing]
        PeerAuth[PeerAuthentication<br/>mTLS STRICT]
        Telemetry[Telemetry<br/>Istio observability]
        ServiceMonitor[ServiceMonitor<br/>Prometheus]
        SMMR[ServiceMeshMemberRoll<br/>Maistra]
    end

    subgraph "External Dependencies"
        KServe[KServe Operator<br/>v0.11.0]
        Istio[Istio/Service Mesh<br/>v1.17.4]
        Authorino[Authorino<br/>v0.15.0]
        Knative[Knative Serving<br/>v0.39.3]
        Prometheus[Prometheus Operator<br/>v0.64.1]
        K8sAPI[Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP]
    end

    User[User/CI] -->|creates| InferenceService
    InferenceService -->|watched by| MainController
    ServingRuntime -->|watched by| MainController
    KnativeService -->|validated by| WebhookValidator
    DSC -->|read by| MainController
    DSCI -->|read by| MainController

    MainController -->|creates via API| Route
    Serverless -->|creates| AuthConfig
    Serverless -->|creates| NetworkPolicy
    Serverless -->|creates| VirtualService
    Serverless -->|creates| PeerAuth
    Serverless -->|creates| Telemetry
    Serverless -->|creates| ServiceMonitor
    Serverless -->|updates| SMMR

    MainController -->|watches via| K8sAPI
    Serverless -->|integrates| Istio
    Serverless -->|integrates| Authorino
    Serverless -->|integrates| Knative
    MonitoringReconciler -->|integrates| Prometheus
    MainController -->|depends on| KServe

    style MainController fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:3px
    style Serverless fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333
    style ModelMesh fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333
    style RawDeploy fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333
    style WebhookValidator fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333
    style InferenceService fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Route fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style AuthConfig fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style VirtualService fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style PeerAuth fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style KServe fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style Istio fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style Authorino fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style Knative fill:#999,stroke:#333
